<template>
    <router-link class="nav-link" :to="link" v-if="!isExternal(link)" :exact="link === '/'">{{
        item.text
    }}</router-link>
    <a
        v-else
        :href="link"
        class="nav-link"
        :target="isMailto(link) ? null : '_blank'"
        :rel="isMailto(link) ? null : 'noopener noreferrer'"
        >{{ item.text }}</a
    >
</template>

<script>
import { isExternal, isMailto, ensureExt } from './util'

export default {
    props: {
        item: {
            required: true
        }
    },
    computed: {
        link() {
            return ensureExt(this.item.link)
        }
    },
    methods: {
        isExternal,
        isMailto
    }
}
</script>
